metadata.name: the ability of Wang Xian
metadata.description:
thing he can do is to help the people of the Dragon Kingdom to do more hidden occupations. After all, he is also a daydreamer in his previous life, thinking of switching to hidden occupations and soaring to the sky.



So, when there is nothing to do, Wang Xian will find those hidden occupation of the post to see.



As a result, Wang Xian knows where to find and how to do some of the tasks.



It was the only way the King could help the Dragon Kingdom.
